  "body": "Currently the pending block looks as follows:\n\n``` js\n\"{\n  \"number\": 33,\n  \"hash\": \"0xddbde8715485d343640ce8cbe9d7c162a4ddce25949f289add4c2b08e4bc7e23\",\n  \"parentHash\": \"0x9189026494323cd572434e5acc21b36c9304558ba23b54d4ecadd0f4967797e6\",\n  \"nonce\": \"0x0000000000000000\",\n  \"sha3Uncles\": \"0x1dcc4de8dec75d7aab85b567b6ccd41ad312451b948a7413f0a142fd40d49347\",\n  \"logsBloom\": \"\",\n  \"transactionsRoot\": \"0x56e81f171bcc55a6ff8345e692c0f86e5b48e01b996cadc001622fb5e363b421\",\n  \"stateRoot\": \"0x54dda68af07643f68739a6e9612ad157a26ae7e2ce81f77842bb5835fbcde583\",\n  \"miner\": \"0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"132480\",\n  \"totalDifficulty\": \"0\",\n  \"size\": 511,\n  \"extraData\": \"0x\",\n  \"gasLimit\": 3141592,\n  \"gasUsed\": 0,\n  \"timestamp\": 1429872279,\n  \"transactions\": [],\n  \"uncles\": []\n}\"\n```\n\nIt would be good to return `null` for the following properties, so that developers can better test against pending blocks (and also to be consistent with pending logs):\n\nFor the block:\n- miner\n- logsBloom\n- nonce\n",
